{"tid":1579444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急！！其實和你塞應該要點搞？","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T15:23:07.000Z","uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd9ec2143007d6bb1624d25cd80b3b8295a7f3e","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"p牌廢青識嘢少，好少喺行動po提意見<br />\n今次真係忍唔住將自己既憂慮講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到和你塞準備搞第四次，但仲無乜行動po<br />\n有啲心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三次既失敗係衰在<br />\n1）人數唔夠<br />\n2）比較多人未有心理準備俾狗截查/抄牌<br />\n3）地理上好難走<br />\n<br />\n雖然有人講 唔走咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁和你塞變相可能係短期佔領機場<br />\n而其實短期又好長期又好<br />\n點都有人因為各種原因要出返黎<br />\n（正如當年佔中都好少可有人佔足咁多日一樣）<br />\n<br />\n另外我見到和你塞一次俾一次難玩<br />\n深深認同人數唔夠係一個大大大問題<br />\n眼見機場文宣方面剩係叫人嗰日留意channel<br />\n缺乏解釋嗰日要點去應對各種問題<br />\n和理非應該有乜準備<br />\n心情非常焦急<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好唔希望一個計劃草率咁出現<br />\n之後因為舊有問題未解決，和理非驚咗入機場<br />\n然後人少，對家又愈玩愈熟<br />\n最後導致好多手足俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有冇計仔？剩返幾日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc3b79cdb20bd89405da447a49e21ffca3e8613","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"1/20"},{"pid":"4491ce4d8001f4144db62502c1ea951a9bb7e714","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8324d35effd9c9837fbe6da930bfbaab13515ab0","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"p牌有冇人睇"},{"pid":"0e4422f44bf014c492a205099286f68795744704","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79b42b1eb23faa6fafe9f6ee8a4a2909392176c","tid":1579444,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"塞，可以塞好多樣野<br />\n唔一定係個條交通輸紐塞<br />\n<br />\n可以係冇野食啦<br />\n冇巴士車長番工啦<br />\n冇電啦<br />\n冇水啦<br />\n冇冷氣啦<br />\n<br />\n塞車好似都會俾人拉<br />\n塞電力呢？塞遊客呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實人既需要都不外乎衣食住行<br />\n惡意收購係自由市場係合法<br />\n<br />\n塞，唔洗做犯法野既"},{"pid":"843bed51a79c51937f74bae7bba24e12d9241635","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e79b42b1eb23faa6fafe9f6ee8a4a2909392176c","tid":1579444,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"塞，可以塞好多樣野<br />\n唔一定係個條交通輸紐塞<br />\n<br />\n可以係冇野食啦<br />\n冇巴士車長番工啦<br />\n冇電啦<br />\n冇水啦<br />\n冇冷氣啦<br />\n<br />\n塞車好似都會俾人拉<br />\n塞電力呢？塞遊客呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實人既需要都不外乎衣食住行<br />\n惡意收購係自由市場係合法<br />\n<br />\n塞，唔洗做犯法野既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"字面上明明地，但要點實行我就唔係好知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7062cec74949ff64b9192fc10c1837a4649ed1","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f688274efde68e8f499753b8100742abfb6cb687","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ce4d9bb6d2d9fb9ad46dde7a857b85cb888c90","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531959d20ab89c6d9ae62be388cc55d9a2cd6af6","tid":1579444,"uid":267123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.